check by using django-admin --version

to install create & activate virtual env 
then install django

Code for virtualenv creation - virtualenv venv
to activate - source venv/bin/activate
then use deactivate to deactivate
to install use pip install django

django project - may contain multiple project application means a group of application
An application is a part of django project 
